contentrichtext.text: :''See also: [[Saint-Barthélemy]]'' {{Infobox French commune |name = Saint-Barthélemy |region = [[Aquitaine]] |department = [[Landes (department)|Landes]] |arrondissement = Dax |canton = Saint-Martin-de-Seignanx |INSEE = 40251 |postal code = 40390 |mayor = |term = |intercommunality = Seignanx |longitude = -1.3303 |latitude = 43.515 |elevation m = 18 |elevation min m = 0 |elevation max m = 71 |area km2 = 5.66 |population = 236 |population date = 1999 }} '''Saint-Barthélemy''' is a [[Communes of France|commune]] in the [[Landes (department)|Landes]] [[Departments of France|department]] in [[Aquitaine]] in south-western [[France]]. ==See also== *[[Communes of the Landes department]] ==References== * [http://www.insee.fr/fr/methodes/nomenclatures/cog/fichecommunale.asp?codedep=40&codecom=251 INSEE commune file] {{Reflist}} {{Landes communes}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Saint-Barthelemy, Landes}} [[Category:Communes of Landes (department)|Saintbarthelemy]] {{Landes-geo-stub}}
